a husband calls 911,

18:57.094 --> 18:57.886
saying his wife
fall down the stairs

18:57.970 --> 19:00.055
but was still breathing,
hurry up.

19:00.138 --> 19:02.891
Husband calls back
five minutes later

19:02.975 --> 19:04.643
checking in on an ETA,

19:04.726 --> 19:06.228
says she's
not breathing anymore.

