-Candace?

21:16.191 --> 21:17.275
Hello?

21:18.068 --> 21:19.528
Is Mark there?

21:19.611 --> 21:20.862
No, he just left for work.

21:20.946 --> 21:22.364
Uh, I need
his car phone then.

21:23.156 --> 21:24.700
Is everything okay?

21:24.783 --> 21:26.284
I just need,
need to speak with Mark.

21:26.368 --> 21:30.205
Alright.
It's, uh, 804-554-3212.

21:30.288 --> 21:33.834
I'll call you back. Okay?
Is that okay?

21:33.917 --> 21:35.752
Is everything okay?
This feels strange.

21:35.836 --> 21:37.629
Please, I really can't talk.

21:37.713 --> 21:38.880
I'll just--
I'll call you back.

21:40.966 --> 21:41.216
Fuck!

21:59.526 --> 22:01.528
-Mark Hello.
-Mark, it's Mike.

22:01.611 --> 22:02.404
Oh, hey, Mike.

22:02.487 --> 22:05.365
How are you doing
this morning?

22:05.449 --> 22:07.784
I couldn't tell Candace.

22:07.868 --> 22:11.705
